name: Espresso_Bookcase_and_Cabinet
description:
The espresso bookcase and cabinet is versatile and contemporary with ample storage. This elegant piece is laminated in melamine which is stain, heat and scratch resistant and sure to compliment any home or office. This one of a kind bookcase has three shelves to accommodate books and accessories, and concealed storage compartment with two doors and chrome metal handles.
